To run this project you must be in the assignment3 directory
Make sure you have python3 and all the related packages

Run the main program by tying into the command line:
python .\main.py

The menu reprints after every command
First enter the number for your option and then follow the instructions
ex.) for 8 - Scale enter the amounts you want to scale and then the x and y and z it should be centered on